Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.76,0:02:34.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我梦到了孩提时分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.70,0:02:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是被我忘却多年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.87,0:02:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直没能忆起的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.38,0:02:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远往昔的…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.07,0:02:50.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…梦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 黑桐鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.77,0:04:19.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是16岁的见习魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.68,0:04:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有黑桐干也这个哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:25.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,苍崎橙子这个老师
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和两仪式这个情敌
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.26,0:04:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是所谓少女的烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.15,0:04:39.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了避免误会 我补充一句
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.44,0:04:43.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我并不是因为爱上了亲哥哥而烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.39,0:04:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是真心的 正经的 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连自己都觉得无可救药的喜欢着黑桐干也
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.72,0:04:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是做叔叔的养女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.83,0:04:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,升入寄宿制的礼园
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.19,0:04:59.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是特意两地分居
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.83,0:05:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是为了让干也忘记我是他妹妹的策略
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.53,0:05:09.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 我目前只有一个烦恼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:15.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个半道杀出来横刀夺爱的臭女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.63,0:05:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.76,0:05:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我·回·来·了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:26.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎回来 鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.36,0:05:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.00,0:05:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了 鲜花是第一次见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来介绍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.67,0:05:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是我的同班同学 两仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要尽快拆散她和干也
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.16,0:05:43.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让干也远离危险的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.86,0:05:49.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了在身心上都能和她抗衡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.94,0:05:52.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我甚至拜入了魔术师的门下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.69,0:05:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我这个坚强女孩的故事…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.00,0:06:00.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.83,0:06:06.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能给我一个解释吗 橙子小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.19,0:06:08.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 看来是顺利送到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.90,0:06:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密武器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.69,0:06:13.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里是秘密武器了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.58,0:06:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得委托内容吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.06,0:06:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出并驱除在礼园操纵妖精使学生不安的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.89,0:06:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.96,0:06:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样一来 看不到妖精的鲜花会需要眼目吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.98,0:06:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.30,0:06:41.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵照苍崎橙子小姐的吩咐前来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.90,0:06:44.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下两仪式
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.82,0:06:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一上来就有波澜四起的预感了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.13,0:06:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不会发生的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.70,0:07:03.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为式把鲜花当妹妹看待嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:06.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还搞不清状况呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:08.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么状况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.96,0:07:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.23,0:07:20.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就怀疑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:24.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子其实脑子不太灵光吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.35,0:07:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:28.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏把你送进学园里
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.52,0:07:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是常人的作为
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.95,0:07:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真过分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.27,0:07:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次的牺牲者无疑是我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.51,0:07:38.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正月还没出
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:41.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就要来帮忙找妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.42,0:07:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:49.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不巧 我没有你和橙子那样的魔眼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.16,0:07:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 这家伙是鲜花的狗吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.14,0:07:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去房间时跟过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.63,0:08:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 它是和家人去海外旅行了的室友 濑尾的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.98,0:08:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在由我代为照顾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.56,0:08:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但它和主子一样调皮 让我头疼得很
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.13,0:08:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里校规这么严 却让养宠物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.83,0:08:32.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么可能让养！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.89,0:08:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么要把它带出来？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.97,0:08:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还能为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.34,0:08:37.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才不是说过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.89,0:08:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快把它送回屋去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.33,0:08:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.88,0:08:58.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是寄宿制学校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.53,0:09:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寒假也有很多学生留校
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.18,0:09:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,千万不要做出引人注目的行动…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.88,0:09:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那里是礼拜堂哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:09.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会做弥撒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.22,0:09:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.75,0:09:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天之爱子 吾等之父 之类的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.98,0:09:18.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爱他能怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.11,0:09:21.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 难道是天之骄子吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.97,0:09:32.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 我先去问问一年级四班的班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个叫叶山的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.58,0:09:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 叶山老师11月突然消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.19,0:09:42.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据说他和危险分子有来往
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.85,0:09:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能已经沉在东京湾底了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.39,0:09:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,300)}{\fscx80\fscy80}请不要随便喂食
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种人也能当老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.48,0:09:52.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为他是理事长的弟弟嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.47,0:09:56.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 现在的班主任是谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.17,0:10:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是玄雾老师
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是一年级一班的黑桐鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知修道院长向您提起过了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.01,0:10:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夺取记忆的妖精？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 有几个学生找我谈过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:33.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 老师怎么处理的？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.33,0:10:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精只是喜欢恶作剧罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让她们别太担心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.69,0:10:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您相信吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精的传说在日本可能不太多
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.26,0:10:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但在欧洲却很是流行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.19,0:10:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师是威尔士出身吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.39,0:10:57.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 在我的故乡 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:11:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多猫妖精犬妖精之类的可爱妖精的传说
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.63,0:11:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也蛮喜欢的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.72,0:11:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您听说过妖精杀人事件吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:27.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是指橘佳织同学一事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.57,0:11:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据四班同学称 她不是自杀的 而是被妖精袭击了…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.80,0:11:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.38,0:11:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 黄路同学 已经这么晚了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.70,0:11:45.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 皐月老师
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.63,0:11:48.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约定的一点早就过了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:54.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间不是永远都有的 要合理利用才行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是学生会长 黄路美沙夜前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是理事长的千金
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.68,0:11:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄路同学真严格
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.44,0:12:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然提道了「永远」这种深奥的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学一事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该不是妖精所为
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.10,0:12:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是黑桐同学吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.39,0:12:17.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.56,0:12:21.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皐月老师和你所调查的没有关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.13,0:12:24.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要打扰他
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.31,0:12:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为当事人的一年级四班学生是没法指望了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.83,0:12:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都不愿提起事件的经过
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.32,0:13:00.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能另辟蹊径了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.40,0:13:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 式
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:13.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄雾老师很像干也 把你吓了一跳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.68,0:13:18.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以你在他面前也很能装乖呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你话里有话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.78,0:13:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.02,0:13:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就事论事罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:30.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 他是玄雾皐月
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.34,0:13:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有多像 他也不是黑桐干也
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.22,0:13:38.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,与其说像 不如说…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.72,0:14:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.72,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.56,0:14:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 式
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要自作主张…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.84,0:14:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:17.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.28,0:14:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐鲜花同学
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.38,0:15:25.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.64,0:15:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心感冒哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.01,0:15:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干… 干也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.53,0:15:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.35,0:15:37.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我打
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.30,0:15:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然搞什么啊 你这个笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒过来了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.80,0:15:50.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜花 你知道现在几点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.75,0:15:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚过下午两点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.99,0:16:04.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式 我难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:07.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妖精夺去了记忆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.64,0:16:19.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是哪里的魔术师 我都要好好修理你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.97,0:16:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算哭着求我 也决不轻饶！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.41,0:16:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜花还蛮大胆的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.44,0:16:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理事长去出席新年会了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.53,0:16:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天之前绝对回不来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:50.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？ 只有这里上锁了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.77,0:16:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.74,0:17:16.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.63,0:17:23.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主啊 感谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.34,0:17:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘佳织事件之后
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.43,0:17:47.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以一年级四班学生为对象的内部问讯资料
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.26,0:17:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘佳织同学自从升入二年级 就有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.10,0:17:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她突然瘦了下来 脸色也不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.30,0:18:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像一直在害怕着什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.82,0:18:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事件当天也在课堂上…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.83,0:18:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精… 妖精要来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.30,0:18:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.62,0:18:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 橘！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.70,0:18:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其后 旧校舍就着火了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明有这么确凿的证言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.40,0:18:27.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在却说不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.72,0:18:30.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是操纵妖精的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.95,0:18:32.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想把橘佳织一案抹消掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.81,0:18:35.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶山果然可疑
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.10,0:18:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就不是好人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.45,0:18:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.96,0:18:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 橙子小姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.56,0:19:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样 今天见到的人里有可疑者吗 式
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.57,0:19:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被妖精夺去的记忆 再也取不回来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.30,0:19:39.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该是 问这个干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.80,0:19:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 少点记忆又不会死人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.09,0:19:45.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是最好的例子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.46,0:19:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 妖精操纵者的目的不在于杀人？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.09,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.65,0:19:55.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多半只是结果变成那样罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.79,0:20:00.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再说了 要生要杀都不必借助妖精之手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:03.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.40,0:20:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊 夺取记忆只表明…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望别人忘记某些事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.08,0:20:12.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要隐瞒某些事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.78,0:20:25.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式 你藏了什么东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.12,0:20:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少装傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我让你把从食堂偷的刀子交出来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过是把刀子 没什么好在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.28,0:20:41.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.12,0:20:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是会用尺子杀锁的那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是收藏起来观赏的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.05,0:20:49.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不论如何你都不打算交出来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很烦耶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.43,0:20:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.63,0:20:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要来硬的了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.16,0:20:58.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我 快点
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你交出来 可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.15,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.98,0:21:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.53,0:21:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋蛮力女！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.72,0:21:13.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.38,0:21:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 看你的力气足够推倒干也了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.42,0:21:22.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你… 你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.32,0:21:24.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 没别的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.54,0:21:27.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想到什么说什么罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.76,0:21:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然被发现了？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.05,0:21:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.32,0:21:37.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我察觉到的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.46,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少当事者本人没发觉到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样不就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.30,0:21:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.63,0:21:52.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种人有什么好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.59,0:21:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们不是兄妹吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.85,0:22:01.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说实话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.01,0:22:05.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜欢特别的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或者说
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.12,0:22:10.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我容易被所谓的「禁忌」吸引
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.12,0:22:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 心上人是近亲这件事
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.78,0:22:15.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我看来是幸运的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.01,0:22:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个变态
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.15,0:22:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 你这不正常的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.43,0:22:28.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题在于
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.63,0:22:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是什么时候喜欢上干也的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.66,0:22:34.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时的事情完全不记得了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.83,0:22:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.87,0:22:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起床
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.80,0:22:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.36,0:22:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是说过今天一早就要去看旧校舍的放火现场吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.14,0:22:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快起来 笨蛋式！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.67,0:22:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 睡死你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.85,0:23:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐小姐 在吗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.16,0:23:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你哥哥来电话了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.05,0:23:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.27,0:23:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.34,0:23:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神 开始调查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.42,0:23:33.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去年11月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘佳织大喊着妖精来了 从教室里飞奔出去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.22,0:23:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跑进了这所旧校舍
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:42.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.30,0:23:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她在这里放了火 企图自我了断
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.23,0:23:51.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精操纵者把相关记忆从学生那里夺去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.67,0:23:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔术师的目的到底是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.91,0:24:10.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐同学 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.41,0:24:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 黄路前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.03,0:24:15.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里见面还真是巧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.15,0:24:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和我一起去做早礼拜吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.14,0:24:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 若不会妨碍到您的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.71,0:24:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.48,0:24:40.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经好久没有像这样两人做礼拜了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.21,0:24:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若没有那次事件
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.09,0:24:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子现在想必也会在我旁边吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.08,0:24:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘佳织吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.18,0:24:50.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.91,0:24:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织对我来说 就像亲妹妹一样
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.93,0:24:56.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然做事不得要领
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.13,0:24:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总是扮演吃亏的角色
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.83,0:25:03.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但那孩子比任何人都要虔诚 都要温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.59,0:25:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.14,0:25:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想把她耻辱的痕迹全部抹去
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.44,0:25:23.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.50,0:25:26.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了佳织
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.12,0:25:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我学了魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.47,0:25:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请就此收手吧 黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.82,0:25:39.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想和你发生冲突
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.58,0:25:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是前辈先动手的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.45,0:25:46.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以我才知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.39,0:25:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然连理由都不记得
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.44,0:25:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你却发自内心地爱着亲哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.50,0:25:58.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好得很
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.01,0:26:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都被你知道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.10,0:26:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就直说了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.21,0:26:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有喜欢上干也的决定性瞬间的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.48,0:26:15.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我察觉到 就已经喜欢上他了
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.62,0:26:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 若你能摘取出那段记忆的话
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.80,0:26:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以放你一马
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.99,0:26:29.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.87,0:26:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精能夺取的
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.46,0:26:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有本人记得的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.79,0:26:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去的记忆除外
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.49,0:26:39.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人能够采集忘却
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.16,0:26:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:26:41.87,0:26:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说放我一马
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.24,0:26:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我不打算以夺取记忆告终
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.54,0:26:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.93,0:26:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些家伙都该受到惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.80,0:27:04.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无辜的佳织被卷了进去
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.44,0:27:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却没有一个人救她
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.90,0:27:09.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袖手旁观
Dialogue: 0,0:27:09.86,0:27:12.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这本身就是一桩罪过
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.00,0:27:16.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.32,0:27:23.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你 是你把佳织逼上绝路的
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.75,0:27:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快住手 不要靠近我！
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.37,0:27:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.10,0:27:40.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐同学你知道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.99,0:27:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,制作使魔
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.67,0:27:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要有原材料
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.32,0:27:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是个事故
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.61,0:28:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 叶山是…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.77,0:28:10.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧 黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.29,0:28:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在朦胧的睡意中
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.03,0:28:16.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会让你的悲叹再生
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.45,0:28:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.23,0:28:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.01,0:28:23.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜花同学
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.97,0:28:25.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.39,0:28:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥… 哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.52,0:28:29.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.99,0:28:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄雾老师 失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.03,0:28:35.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的脸色不太好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.17,0:28:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.24,0:28:39.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.35,0:28:42.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.22,0:28:43.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还记得
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.82,0:28:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.99,0:28:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.82,0:28:57.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四班学生集体失踪了？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.70,0:28:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非有什么秘密弥撒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.74,0:29:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那怎么可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.74,0:29:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.09,0:29:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄雾老师
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.64,0:29:09.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄路前辈去哪里了 您看见了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.24,0:29:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 除了黑桐同学 我没看到其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.60,0:29:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谈判破裂就马上来硬的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.04,0:29:20.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来硬的？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.52,0:29:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 黄路美沙夜打算消除有关橘佳织的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.30,0:29:27.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连同一年级四班的学生一起
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.40,0:29:32.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式 我们分头找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.78,0:29:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在校内再仔细找一遍
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.10,0:29:38.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去林子里看看 我有点头绪
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.02,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.71,0:29:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 那里什么都没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.62,0:30:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 请当心
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.42,0:30:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.17,0:30:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么会这样…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:18.39,0:31:20.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们被藏到哪里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.72,0:31:25.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定就在这所学校里
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.65,0:31:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且那间教室…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:39.46,0:31:40.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干也…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:42.61,0:31:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是干也的话 会怎么办呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.29,0:31:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是干也的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.75,0:32:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.68,0:32:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.25,0:32:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你怎么不哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.65,0:32:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.76,0:32:44.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好累的 你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.04,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.84,0:32:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 式 发现什么了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:32:51.08,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.54,0:32:54.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.46,0:32:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说鲜花 有你的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.52,0:33:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你老哥打来的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.02,0:33:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于叶山英雄的情报？
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.19,0:33:10.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是式拜托我调查的
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.03,0:33:14.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但还是报告给鲜花比较合适吧
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.69,0:33:18.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 式有拜托哥哥做这种事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.59,0:33:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式说鲜花有些在意叶山这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.67,0:33:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 但我没有拜托她调查
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.71,0:33:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望哥哥扯上这种危险事件
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.55,0:33:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,式一点都不担心哥哥的安全
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.47,0:33:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.28,0:33:41.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在式把全部心思都放在你身上了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.23,0:33:49.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 查到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.64,0:33:53.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那我先从式的委托内容说起
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.20,0:33:55.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后传达橙子小姐的口信
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.54,0:33:58.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.77,0:34:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经照您的吩咐传达给她了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.35,0:34:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.11,0:34:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不用去救她们两个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.61,0:34:21.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄雾皐月不是被称为「伪神之书」的危险魔术师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.44,0:34:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出不了什么大事
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.33,0:34:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他只会用言语支配人的认识
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.37,0:34:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有其他攻击手段
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.44,0:34:33.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对策也教给她了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.29,0:34:34.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹也是我的徒弟 
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.02,0:34:36.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该能搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.71,0:34:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起那个 吃饭 吃饭
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.19,0:35:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.68,0:35:04.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玄雾老师 晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.33,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.92,0:35:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那边什么都没有哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.24,0:35:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有急事 告辞
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.50,0:36:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想让她们采取同样的自杀手段
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.92,0:36:19.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让全班人一起自焚也太过分了吧 前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.74,0:36:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是当然的报应吗 黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:36:24.29,0:36:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情今晚就要结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.90,0:36:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正的幕后黑手也不会来打扰我们
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.84,0:36:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做的事还真是拐弯抹角啊
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.23,0:36:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目的是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.86,0:36:47.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 我只是达成他人的愿望罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.55,0:36:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本次事件只是她们的愿望所致
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.61,0:36:54.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我本人没有什么目的
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.91,0:36:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也是一种缘分呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.23,0:36:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我之所以来这个国家
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.27,0:37:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因为荒耶宗莲拜托过我
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.03,0:37:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我把你忘却的两年前的记忆还来
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.00,0:37:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你也在追寻着失去的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.61,0:37:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我能看到你隐藏在言语之下的真心
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.77,0:37:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的任务仅此而已
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.34,0:37:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄路同学的事情…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.49,0:37:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.16,0:37:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若用人类的话说
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.93,0:37:28.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是单纯的打发时间吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.96,0:37:31.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人需要娱乐才能活下去
Dialogue: 0,0:37:31.87,0:37:35.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若只是单纯地活着 就和机器没什么两样了
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.91,0:37:38.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是魔术师吗
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.96,0:37:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我是操纵言语的魔术师
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.26,0:37:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人称「伪神之书」
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.55,0:37:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩火就到此为止吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:52.43,0:37:54.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄路前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.01,0:37:57.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了 黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.55,0:38:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在还可以一笑了之
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.23,0:38:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经有人死了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.66,0:38:07.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 叶山死了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.46,0:38:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他不是你杀的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.55,0:38:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀死叶山的… 是叶山自己
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.15,0:38:22.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉我这件事的 是妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.81,0:38:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为了佳织而学习魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.67,0:38:28.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并拿叶山做了妖精的原材料
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.74,0:38:33.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 两人为什么看到了不可能存在的妖精的幻觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.58,0:38:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻觉？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.17,0:38:39.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然变瘦 情绪不稳定 出现幻视
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.11,0:38:45.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这完全符合毒瘾发作时的症状
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.98,0:38:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳织无法原谅上瘾的自己 企图自杀
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.58,0:38:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶山在与前辈谈话途中因毒瘾而突发心肌梗塞
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.81,0:38:57.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是说
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.56,0:38:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了叶山英雄自作自受以外
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.88,0:39:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有人死 也没有人杀人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:04.10,0:39:10.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剩下的 只有没能拯救佳织脱离痛苦的人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.24,0:39:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而最想逃避这个事实的…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.36,0:39:20.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以说 你是第一个被夺去记忆的
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.27,0:39:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘却了这一部分
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.44,0:39:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己应当也发觉到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.40,0:39:27.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的复仇…
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.52,0:39:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是你自己期待的 单方面空想！
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.75,0:39:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得好 说得好
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.16,0:39:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.60,0:40:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,AzoLto
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.31,0:40:28.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空想的人是你 黑桐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.62,0:40:32.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我用妖精从四班学生那里问出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.68,0:40:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是毋庸置疑的事实
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.54,0:40:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.64,0:40:40.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.77,0:40:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没能从佳织和叶山那里打听
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.40,0:40:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所谓的真实
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.34,0:40:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是事件结束后产生于学生间的流言
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.00,0:40:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所做的一切都不过是亡羊补牢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.51,0:40:58.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是复仇的动机 还是魔术
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.85,0:41:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而给你力量的…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.68,0:41:22.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你将…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.75,0:41:24.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…迷失前路
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.67,0:41:28.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.06,0:41:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可怕 论厮杀我完全不是对手
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.77,0:41:39.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 愿望会反噬自身
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.26,0:41:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你想起来的瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.10,0:41:44.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发觉的瞬间将宿主吞噬
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.60,0:41:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的忘却也属于这一类
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.08,0:41:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里 看不见
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.35,0:42:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会再生那份悲叹
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.11,0:42:04.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算忘却了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.10,0:42:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但记忆确实被你录音了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.86,0:42:22.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.80,0:42:36.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前辈！
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.81,0:42:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.27,0:42:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,碍事
Dialogue: 0,0:43:20.40,0:43:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别·小·看·我！
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.09,0:43:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还不去死
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.82,0:44:14.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.88,0:44:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.28,0:44:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么去了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.99,0:44:22.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结束了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.26,0:44:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大功告成
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.58,0:44:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.66,0:44:47.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吧 晶
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.31,0:44:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.27,0:45:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了 鲜花
Dialogue: 0,0:45:09.74,0:45:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 事件圆满解决了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.88,0:45:18.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个 我怎么也找不到式
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.45,0:45:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙也有大方的一面嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.61,0:45:27.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她这次努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.42,0:45:28.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该奖励一下
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.49,0:45:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.12,0:45:33.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「伪神之书」
Dialogue: 0,0:45:34.29,0:45:38.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封印指定的魔术师这次也落得一场空呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.65,0:45:39.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橙子小姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.96,0:45:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我转告鲜花 就说干得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.73,0:45:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 我一定转达
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.79,0:46:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 式呢
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.65,0:46:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她先回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.42,0:46:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找她有事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:06.06,0:46:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.73,0:46:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说你听说了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.33,0:46:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘同学恢复意识了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.30,0:46:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.44,0:46:20.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根据证言 10月份叶山发作倒地的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.60,0:46:23.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不巧被橘看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.84,0:46:25.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后 为了封口
Dialogue: 0,0:46:25.71,0:46:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叶山对她注射了毒品
Dialogue: 0,0:46:30.46,0:46:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她也是个被害者
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.07,0:46:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是段悲伤的记忆
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.87,0:46:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能被忘掉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.54,0:47:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.19,0:47:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲜花 不坐车吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.18,0:47:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:47:10.50,0:47:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.85,0:47:17.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这附近有吃东西的地方吗
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.96,0:47:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下坡后有个西餐店
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.63,0:47:21.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很远的
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.80,0:47:26.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁让你前两天放我鸽子 和式出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:26.86,0:47:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被你这么一说…
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.96,0:47:31.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就不要抱怨了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:03.91,0:48:06.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我梦到了孩提时分
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.86,0:48:10.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥和我都很熟悉的…
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.44,0:48:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…重要的人过世了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.57,0:48:16.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然满脸悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.76,0:48:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他一滴泪都没有流
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.77,0:48:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你为什么不哭呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.18,0:48:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 为什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.10,0:48:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为男孩子不能哭吗
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.70,0:48:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 你怎么不哭？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.55,0:48:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使想哭 也不能哭
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.18,0:48:46.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为那是件特别的事
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.41,0:48:50.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这份坚强让我胸口一紧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.54,0:48:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,浑身上下都很普通
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.32,0:48:55.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不会伤害别人
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.79,0:48:57.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和谁都能相互理解
Dialogue: 0,0:48:57.68,0:48:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但谁都没有注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.91,0:49:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空空如也的孤独
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.70,0:49:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时此刻 对于我来说
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.35,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:07.49,0:49:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑桐干也成为了特别的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.18,0:49:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不能失去的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:49:23.11,0:49:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星空之下
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.03,0:49:27.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兄妹二人仰望着群星
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.09,0:49:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是珍藏在我心底的风景画
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.65,0:49:38.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能被忆起的 遥远往昔的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.05,0:55:18.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我讨厌弱者
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.18,0:55:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了毁尸灭迹 选择了吃掉它吗
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.84,0:56:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么没有全部咽下去
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.45,0:56:04.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被身为人类的道德观所束缚了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:08.25,0:56:11.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你为什么动口了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:13.14,0:56:17.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在我看来 那是自然而然的行为
Dialogue: 0,0:56:17.53,0:56:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 这表明你是特别的
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.94,0:56:26.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是特别的？
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.32,0:56:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.84,0:56:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已经不在常识范畴内了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.22,0:56:35.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是说我已经坏掉了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.51,0:56:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 就彻底坏掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.47,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.33,0:57:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个小时吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.35,0:57:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很优秀
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.05,0:57:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但这也是极限了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.78,0:57:21.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发觉到自我起源就只有这种程度了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:21.35,0:57:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若不让起源觉醒 就不会成形
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.10,0:57:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不为任何人所束缚
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.00,0:57:30.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为超越者的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.47,0:57:34.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为脱离常规的生命的特别性
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.86,0:57:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不想要吗
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.43,0:57:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.32,0:57:44.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:47.14,0:57:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.61,0:57:56.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔术师 荒耶宗莲
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.76,0:57:58.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.41,0:58:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.23,0:58:07.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只差一个字
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.22,0:58:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是狮子了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:58:19.41,0:58:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.96,0:58:22.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是笑笑
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.78,0:58:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就好幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.51,0:58:27.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很放心
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.15,0:58:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽管会不安
Dialogue: 0,0:58:30.56,0:58:32.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你在
Dialogue: 0,0:58:32.07,0:58:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是走走
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.80,0:58:35.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:58:36.25,0:58:37.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你近在咫尺
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.97,0:58:40.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又远在天边
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.71,0:58:42.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:58:42.63,0:58:44.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如梦似幻的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.27,0:58:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岁月的 遗痕
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
